      <description>2. Installation &amp;amp; Configuration 문제풀이&#xD;#&#xD;CKA&#xD;#&#xD;#&#xD;1. Deploy a pod named nginx-pod using the nginx:alpine image&#xD;#&#xD;Answer&#xD;$ k run nginx-pod --image=nginx:alpine -o yaml &amp;gt; 1-1.yaml $ k apply -f 1-1.yaml $ k get pods NAME READY STATUS RESTARTS AGE pod/nginx-pod 1/1 Running 0 59s 2. Deploy a messaging pod using the redis:alpine image with the labels set to tier=msg&#xD;#&#xD;Answer&#xD;$ k run messaging --image=redis:alpine --labl=tier=msg -o yaml &amp;gt; 1-2.</description>
